var SortDataByAlphabet = new Class({
    initialize: function(data) {
        this.chineseUnicodeAlphabet = "";
        return this.sortDataByAlphabet(data);
    },
    getAlphabet: function(str) {
        var ctx = this;
        if (typeof (str) != "string") {
            return "";
        }
        var arrResult = [];
        for (var i = 0, len = str.length; i < len; i++) {
            var ch = str.charAt(i);
            arrResult.push(ctx.checkCh(ch));
        }
        return ctx.mkRslt(arrResult);
    },
    checkCh: function(ch) {
        var chineseUnicodeAlphabet = this.chineseUnicodeAlphabet;
        var uni = ch.charCodeAt(0);
        if (uni > 40869 || uni < 19968) {
            return ch;
        }
        return ((chineseUnicodeAlphabet.charAt(uni - 19968)));
    },
    mkRslt: function(arr) {
        var arrRslt = [""];
        for (var i = 0, len = arr.length; i < len; i++) {
            var str = arr[i];
            var strlen = str.length;
            if (strlen == 1) {
                for (var k = 0; k < arrRslt.length; k++) {
                    arrRslt[k] += str;
                }
            } else {
                var tmpArr = arrRslt.slice(0);
                arrRslt = [];
                for (k = 0; k < strlen; k++) {
                    var tmp = tmpArr.slice(0);
                    for (var j = 0; j < tmp.length; j++) {
                        tmp[j] += str.charAt(k);
                    }
                    arrRslt = arrRslt.concat(tmp);
                }
            }
        }
        return arrRslt;
    },
    sortKeysByAlphabet: function(obj) {
        var sortObj = {};
        var sortKeys = Object.keys(obj).sort();
        for (var i = 0; i < sortKeys.length; i++) {
            var key = sortKeys[i];
            sortObj[key] = obj[key];
        }
        return sortObj;
    },
    sortDataByAlphabet: function(data) {
        var ctx = this;
        var result = {};
        for (var i = 0, len = data.length; i < len; i++) {
            var firstCh = data[i][1].substr(0, 1);
            var alphabet = ctx.getAlphabet(firstCh);
            if (result.hasOwnProperty(alphabet)) {
                result[alphabet].push(data[i]);
            } else {
                result[alphabet] = [data[i]]
            }
        }
        return ctx.sortKeysByAlphabet(result);
    }
});
